      <tr>
        <td><code>DataGrid</code></td>
        <td><code>columns, pageData, pageSizeOptions, selectable, onPageChange, onSortChange, onSelectionChange, onRowClick</code></td>
        <td>AG Grid v35 래퍼. Excel/CSV 내보내기 내장.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>SearchForm</code></td>
        <td><code>fields, onSearch, defaultValues</code></td>
        <td>동적 필드 구성. 데이터타입 4종 옵션(VARCHAR/CHAR/NUMERIC/DATETIME) 포함.</td>
