<section id="fe-auth" class="section">
  <div class="page-title">인증 흐름</div>
  <div class="page-subtitle">HttpOnly Cookie JWT · Zustand 전역 상태</div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">인증 방식</div>
    <div class="kv">
      <dt>토큰 저장</dt><dd>HttpOnly Cookie (<code>access_token</code>) — JS 직접 접근 불가</dd>
      <dt>이전 방식</dt><dd><del><code>localStorage['trmdict_token']</code></del> → 2026-05-19 Cookie 방식으로 전환</dd>
      <dt>자동 포함</dt><dd><code>axios.defaults.withCredentials = true</code></dd>
      <dt>401 처리</dt><dd>Axios interceptor → <code>useAuthStore.logout()</code> + <code>/login</code> redirect</dd>
      <dt>403 처리</dt><dd>Axios interceptor → <code>sonner</code> toast 표시</dd>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">ProtectedRoute</div>
    <div class="kv">
      <dt>역할</dt><dd>인증 상태 확인 → 미인증 시 <code>/login</code> redirect</dd>
      <dt>ADMIN check</dt><dd>Import 메뉴 — <code>user.role === 'ADMIN'</code> 확인</dd>
      <dt>적용 범위</dt><dd><code>/home, /domain, /word, /forbidden, /import, /import/:historyId</code></dd>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">useAuthStore (Zustand)</div>
    <div class="kv">
      <dt>State</dt><dd><code>user: { id, username, name, role } | null</code></dd>
      <dt>Actions</dt><dd><code>setUser(user)</code> · <code>logout()</code></dd>
      <dt>초기화</dt><dd>앱 시작 시 <code>GET /api/v1/auth/me</code> 호출 → user 설정</dd>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">로그인 흐름</div>
    <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:2">
      <span style="color:var(--accent2)">1.</span> LoginPage → <code>POST /api/v1/auth/login</code> (username + password)<br>
      <span style="color:var(--accent2)">2.</span> 서버 → HttpOnly Cookie 발급 + <code>LoginResponse(user)</code> 반환<br>
      <span style="color:var(--accent2)">3.</span> <code>useAuthStore.setUser(user)</code> 전역 상태 저장<br>
      <span style="color:var(--accent2)">4.</span> <code>/home</code> redirect<br>
      <br>
      <span style="color:var(--muted)">로그아웃:</span> <code>POST /api/v1/auth/logout</code> → Cookie 만료 → <code>logout()</code> → <code>/login</code>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">Import 폴링 패턴 (DetailPage)</div>
    <div class="kv">
      <dt>폴링 interval</dt><dd>2초</dd>
      <dt>자동 중지</dt><dd>terminal 상태(COMPLETED / PARTIAL_SUCCESS / FAILED) 도달 시</dd>
      <dt>자동 중지</dt><dd>컴포넌트 unmount 시</dd>
      <dt>endpoint</dt><dd><code>GET /api/v1/imports/{historyId}</code></dd>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</div><!-- /content -->
</div><!-- /shell -->

<script>
  function show(id) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.section').forEach(s => s.classList.remove('visible'));
    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-item').forEach(a => a.classList.remove('active'));
    document.getElementById(id).classList.add('visible');
    event.target.classList.add('active');
  }
</script>
</body>
</html>
