  <div class="grid2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">레이어 규칙</div>
      <table>
        <tr><th>레이어</th><th>역할 / 규칙</th></tr>
        <tr><td><code>entity</code></td><td>JPA 영속 객체. Controller 반환 절대 금지.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>dto</code></td><td>Request 전용. <code>*SearchDto</code> / <code>*SaveDto</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>vo</code></td><td>Response 전용. <code>*ListVo</code>(그리드) / <code>*DtlVo</code>(전체 필드 flat)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>repository</code></td><td><code>JpaRepository&lt;Entity, Long&gt;</code> 상속. 인터페이스 분리 없음.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>service</code></td><td>@Transactional. 인터페이스 분리 없음.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>controller</code></td><td>HTTP 바인딩 + @Valid + VO 반환</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">코딩 컨벤션 핵심</div>
      <table>
        <tr><th>항목</th><th>규칙</th></tr>
        <tr><td>들여쓰기</td><td>4칸 스페이스 · 최대 120자</td></tr>
        <tr><td>@Slf4j</td><td>Service · Controller 전체 필수</td></tr>
        <tr><td>@Transactional</td><td>조회 메서드 <code>readOnly=true</code> 필수</td></tr>
        <tr><td>PK 전략</td><td><code>@SequenceGenerator + SEQUENCE</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td>FetchType</td><td><code>LAZY</code> 기본</td></tr>
        <tr><td>NULL 직렬화</td><td><code>@JsonInclude(NON_NULL)</code> VO 전체</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">비동기 작업 인프라 (C1)</div>
    <div class="kv">
      <dt>Bean 이름</dt><dd><code>taskExecutor</code> — <code>AsyncConfig.java</code></dd>
      <dt>스레드 풀</dt><dd>core 2 / max 4 / queue 20 (local) · 50 (prod)</dd>
      <dt>상태 흐름</dt><dd><code>PENDING → RUNNING → COMPLETED | PARTIAL_SUCCESS | FAILED</code></dd>
      <dt>큐 초과</dt><dd><code>RejectedExecutionException</code> → <code>IMPORT_3007</code> (503)</dd>
      <dt>재시작 stale</dt><dd><code>ApplicationReadyEvent</code> — RUNNING/PENDING → FAILED 전환</dd>
      <dt>Shutdown</dt><dd>30초 graceful shutdown</dd>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

